<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实吧，<delay8 />我忘了去练习了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，<delay8 />船到桥头自然直！<delay frames="30" />
