	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大赛<delay8 />已经开始了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鼓足干劲多钓些鱼吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今天晴天，真是太好了！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好了，<delay8 />要开始努力钓鱼了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你好啊！<delay20 />
