可以收获奖杯哦！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />想想都让人热血沸腾啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鱼上钩那瞬间的紧张感<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
通过鱼线传达到手上的<delay8 />毅力与坚持<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />感觉真不错！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很好！<delay frames="30" />我一定要钓到大鱼！<delay frames="40" />
